    <!-- Arachnidas -->
    <ThingDef ParentName="BasePrimitiveMedium">
        <defName>ScramSRP_Pri_Arachnida</defName>
        <label>primitive arachnida</label>
        <description>Assembled from the merging of several assimilated bodies into a larger form. Primitive parasites are the first large parasites to appear during infestation.\n\nAn arachnoid assemblage of the deceased. Though its abdomen is weak, it can create silk as tough as steel, used to latch onto and drag hapless victims into its claws. Precursor to greater forms.</description>
